Package com.samczsun.skype4j.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ChatNotFoundException
    Represents an exception which is thrown when an attempt is made to load a chat which does not exist
    ConnectionException
    Thrown when an exception occurs while connecting to an endpoint
    InvalidCredentialsException
    Thrown when invalid credentials are given to log in
    NestedSkypeException
    Represents a SkypeException which holds another exception as the cause
    NoPermissionException
    Thrown if an operation was attempted which required admin privileges
    NoSuchContactException  
    NotLoadedException
    Thrown when a chat is not yet loaded but an operation to modify it or read values was attempted
    NotParticipatingException  
    ParseException
    Thrown when parsing of a response from Skype Web fails
    SkypeException
    Represents any exception that may occur while using this API
